  +files/4.0.9/config.tcl, aolserver-4.0.8.ebuild, +aolserver-4.0.9.ebuild:
  Bumped to 4.0.9. files/ reorganized a little also

  05 Jan 2005; Ian Leitch <port001@gentoo.org> files/4.0.8/Makefile.global,
  aolserver-4.0.8.ebuild:
  Changed ns_conf to /usr/share/aolserver/include and fixed up Makefiles in
  preperation for an aolserver eclass

  19 Dec 2004; Sven Wegener <swegener@gentoo.org> aolserver-4.0.8.ebuild:
